                <h1>Do All Jobs Require Background Checks? Here's What You Need to Know!</h1>
                <p>Not all jobs conduct background checks, but many employers do to ensure candidate reliability and safety. Industries like healthcare, finance, and education commonly perform these checks due to the sensitive nature of the work. However, small businesses or less regulated jobs may not prioritize them.</p>
